{"type":"message","id":"ab0f6696","parentId":"bb1e4738","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:25:23.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据搜索结果，我找到了三个模型的最新信息：\n\n1. **Qwen3.5-Plus** (via OpenRouter):\n   - Input: $0.26 per million tokens\n   - Output: $1.56 per million tokens\n   - Context window: 需要进一步确认，但 Qwen Plus 支持 1M tokens\n\n2. **MiniMax-M2.5**:\n   - Input: $0.20-$0.30 per million tokens (OpenRouter 显示 $0.20，artificialanalysis 显示 $0.30)\n   - Output: $1.20 per million tokens\n   - Context window: 196,608 tokens (~200K)\n\n3. **Kimi K2.5**:\n   - Input: $0.45-$0.60 per million tokens\n   - Output: $2.20-$3.00 per million tokens\n   - Context window: 256K-262K tokens\n\n让我再搜索一下 Qwen3.5-Plus 的具体 context window 信息，以及确认阿里云官方的定价。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cabda79332fb4de783c59fda","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://openrouter.ai/qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","extractMode":"text","maxChars":3000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1447bceafa574d2a97bfeb96","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://platform.moonshot.ai/docs/pricing/chat","extractMode":"text","maxChars":3000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773995116953}}
