ws outlets, the industry has a new benchmark for what “native multimodality” looks like. This model isn&#x27;t just an incremental update; it is a foundational shift in how MiniMax approaches the Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) architecture to deliver frontier-level intelligence at scale. MiniMax M2.5 is built upon a sophisticated technical foundation that distinguishes it from previous iterations and many contemporary competitors. Unlike “stitched” models that use separate encoders for vision or audio, MiniMax M2.5 is natively multimodal.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"daf3e2640811c659\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 12, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"vertu.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"677ac18695520c3c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMiniMax\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"677ac18695520c3c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.minimax.io/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e4358b0f9bdbf456\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMiniMax has independently developed ... as ultra-long context processing, <strong>capable of understanding, generating, and integrating multiple modalities including text, audio, image, video, and music</strong>....\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e4358b0f9bdbf456\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"November 30, 2021\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.minimax.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"800741526b388fef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMiniMax-M2.5 - Intelligence, Performance & Price Analysis\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"800741526b388fef\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://artificialanalysis.ai/models/minimax-m2-5\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0daf0e2d2257c67d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>No, MiniMax-M2.5 is not multimodal</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0daf0e2d2257c67d\\\">>>\",\n