{"type":"message","id":"13aaf659","parentId":"b78e7fae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:28:21.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 cacheRead 和 cacheWrite 的定价。我需要搜索阿里云 DashScope 的上下文缓存定价政策，以及 MiniMax 和 Moonshot 的缓存定价。\n\n根据之前获取的阿里云百炼定价页面信息，提到了\"若模型支持上下文缓存，仅输入 Token 享有折扣\"，但具体缓存读取和写入的价格需要进一步确认。\n\n让我搜索一下各家的缓存定价政策。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7dd27d8e658846e7bddc1558","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"阿里云 DashScope 上下文缓存 cache pricing 2026","count":3}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_512fc6ff0b7045938768bcc6","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"MiniMax API context cache pricing cost","count":3}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c07f57d546b74d36b62d6f4a","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Kimi Moonshot context cache pricing cost","count":3}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773995297273}}
